{"name":"文章","postlist":[{"title":"父爱如山，母爱如水","slug":"19","date":"2020-06-21","updated":"2020-06-21","path":"api/posts/37265.json","excerpt":"<p>&#8195;&#8195; 家是温暖的港湾，父亲是伟岸的大山，挺直了我人生的高度，母亲是溪流，包容了我的自私。儿行千里岂止母担忧，父亲鬓角的白发，叫我如何报答。步步走来，尽是沧桑，母亲的微笑无不在我的身边。每当面临崩溃，父亲的肩膀撑起了倒下的我。</p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5eef162014195aa59443e1c3.png","content":null,"min2read":5,"word4post":"1.6k","url":"/posts/37265/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"想说的话","path":"api/tags/想说的话.json","url":"/tags/想说的话/"},{"name":"父亲节","path":"api/tags/父亲节.json","url":"/tags/父亲节/"}]},{"title":"许我一剪菩提光阴","slug":"18","date":"2020-06-07","updated":"2020-06-07","path":"api/posts/17428.json","excerpt":"<p>　　秋风，清凉，是一叶菩提的洁净，轻轻拂落，飘落在我们心中的尘……</p> <p align=\"right\"> ——题记","cover":null,"content":null,"min2read":4,"word4post":"1.3k","url":"/posts/17428/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"},{"name":"散文","path":"api/categories/散文.json","url":"/categories/文章/散文/"}],"tags":[{"name":"散文","path":"api/tags/散文.json","url":"/tags/散文/"},{"name":"文章","path":"api/tags/文章.json","url":"/tags/文章/"}]},{"title":"遇见温暖，遇见你","slug":"17","date":"2020-05-21","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/11546.json","excerpt":"<p></p><p>　一生至少该有一次，为了某个人而忘了自己。不求有结果，不求同行，不求曾经拥有，甚至不求你爱我。只求在最美的年华里，遇到你。</p><p>　　——题记 </p>","cover":true,"content":null,"min2read":5,"word4post":"1.6k","url":"/posts/11546/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"遇见","path":"api/tags/遇见.json","url":"/tags/遇见/"}]},{"title":"母亲节","slug":"16","date":"2020-05-10","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/9851.json","excerpt":"<p></p><p> 有一种情，从我呱呱落地起，始终不渝，那就是母亲不求回报的爱。</p></p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5eb6692ec2a9a83be5bd03e5.jpg","content":null,"min2read":4,"word4post":"1.3k","url":"/posts/9851/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"母亲节","path":"api/tags/母亲节.json","url":"/tags/母亲节/"},{"name":"想说的话","path":"api/tags/想说的话.json","url":"/tags/想说的话/"}]},{"title":"你若静谧，风雅自来","slug":"08","date":"2020-04-28","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/60704.json","excerpt":"<p>　　晓光迷蒙，择取幽径，悠然行走。绿荫深处，不闻人语响，但闻啼鸟鸣。静谧深处，是心灵最真最深的抵达，是灵魂得以翩跹的地方。我想，但凡深知生命的人，都会努力追寻内心的声音；但凡深知自己内心的人，必定性情娴静高 <br>　　你若静谧，风雅自来。</p>","cover":"https://cn.bing.com/th?id=OHR.BWFlipper_ZH-CN1813139386_1920x1080.jpg&rf=LaDigue_1920x1080.jpg&pid=hp","content":null,"min2read":3,"word4post":979,"url":"/posts/60704/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"},{"name":"散文","path":"api/categories/散文.json","url":"/categories/文章/散文/"}],"tags":[{"name":"散文","path":"api/tags/散文.json","url":"/tags/散文/"},{"name":"文章","path":"api/tags/文章.json","url":"/tags/文章/"}]},{"title":"忽闻春将暮，花开也多情","slug":"6","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/60347.json","excerpt":"<p> 伴着流动的白云，溢彩的霞光，走进初夏的明媚苍绿里，用热烈的心情，去拥抱新的夏季，懂得在每一个遇见的季节里爱并珍惜。<br></p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5ea29129c2a9a83be5531490.jpg","content":null,"min2read":5,"word4post":"1.6k","url":"/posts/60347/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"},{"name":"春色","path":"api/tags/春色.json","url":"/tags/春色/"}]},{"title":"惜春","slug":"7","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/50231.json","excerpt":"<p> 黄昏清水阁、依旧窗半开 </p>","cover":null,"content":null,"min2read":"1","word4post":189,"url":"/posts/50231/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"},{"name":"遇见","path":"api/tags/遇见.json","url":"/tags/遇见/"}]},{"title":"遇见你，就是最好时光","slug":"4","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/9004.json","excerpt":"<p> 最好的爱情，也许就是相互珍惜，还有彼此的懂得和灵魂深处的契合吧！</p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5ea2913cc2a9a83be5532ac5.jpg","content":null,"min2read":3,"word4post":951,"url":"/posts/9004/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"},{"name":"遇见","path":"api/tags/遇见.json","url":"/tags/遇见/"}]},{"title":"想你","slug":"09","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/17220.json","excerpt":"<p> <strong><em> 想你，每每午夜时分，涌上心头······</em></strong></p><p> 思念一段时光的掌纹，躲在某一时间，某一地点，想念一个站在来路也站在去路的让我牵挂的人。<br> 有时候常在反思，原来，关于想你这件事，躲得过对酒当歌的夜，躲不过四下无人的街。<br></p>","cover":true,"content":null,"min2read":1,"word4post":538,"url":"/posts/17220/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"},{"name":"想你","path":"api/tags/想你.json","url":"/tags/想你/"}]},{"title":"清浅的夏日，遇见恰好的你","slug":"3","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/37841.json","excerpt":"<p>&ensp; &ensp; &ensp; 一缕微风摇曳叶的绿意；一阵细雨清新花的艳丽。</p><p> &ensp; &ensp; &ensp; 季节的风总是给人回忆给人期许；红尘的雨总是给人浪漫给人惊喜。你是一朵蝴蝶飞进我的心窗；你是一泓清泉流进我的心底。</p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5ea2913cc2a9a83be5532ac5.jpg","content":null,"min2read":4,"word4post":"1.2k","url":"/posts/37841/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"}]},{"title":"且敬往事一杯酒，故事与你不强留","slug":"2","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/2199.json","excerpt":"<p>&ensp; &ensp; &ensp; 不知是时光冲淡了回忆，还是回忆遗忘了时光。闲暇之时，偶然也会回首那些逝去的岁月，光影交错，似流水斑斓，却已是再也无法挽回的时光。</p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5ea290b6c2a9a83be552997c.jpg","content":null,"min2read":3,"word4post":"1.1k","url":"/posts/2199/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"}]},{"title":"缘起则聚，缘灭则散","slug":"1","date":"2020-04-26","updated":"2020-05-21","path":"api/posts/39718.json","excerpt":"<p>&ensp; &ensp; &ensp; 曾经以为，相爱的人一定要相守，只有相守，情感才能长久。可是，此岸和彼岸只不过是空间的差距，却无法拉长心灵的距离。</p>","cover":"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5ea290b6c2a9a83be552996b.jpg","content":null,"min2read":7,"word4post":"2.3k","url":"/posts/39718/","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json","url":"/categories/文章/"}],"tags":[{"name":"逸轩","path":"api/tags/逸轩.json","url":"/tags/逸轩/"}]}]}